Feature: Reviews
  In order to tell my friends what I think about a restaurant
  As a user
  I want to write reviews

  Scenario: Write a review
    Given there is a "Restaurant" named "Test Restaurant"
      And I am logged in
      And my profile is complete
      And I create a review for "Test Restaurant"
     Then a review should exist for "Test Restaurant"
      And I should see it on the restaurant page for "Test Restaurant"
      And I should see a review for "Test Restaurant" on my profile
